com.solacesystems.jcsmp.impl.client

Class ClientInfoProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.solacesystems.jcsmp.impl.client.ClientInfoProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JMSClientInfoProvider

    public class ClientInfoProvider
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Provides client information and description.

    If an application (ex: SolJMS) needs to override client information, subclass this and give an instance of your own ClientInfoProvider in JCSMPProperties using the SECRET property key {link JCSMPProperties.CLIENT_INFO_PROVIDER. 

     sessionProp.setProperty(JCSMPProperties.CLIENT_INFO_PROVIDER, new MyInfoProvider());
